1. **`applyForces`** â€” Coulomb repulsion between all node pairs + Hooke's law spring attraction along edges + centripetal gravity toward canvas center
2. **`emitParticle`** â€” spawns particles from random nodes with random velocity vectors
3. **`updateParticles`** â€” integrates particle positions with velocity decay, culling expired particles
4. **`smoothCamera`** â€” lerps the camera toward a target position using exponential easing (`theta`)
5. **`tick`** â€” main loop at ~60fps (16ms interval), emitting a particle every 3rd frame
